thread.title: Brazil's Vale produced 85.3 mln tonnes of iron ore in 2nd-qtr
thread.title_full: Brazil's Vale produced 85.3 mln tonnes of iron ore in 2nd-qtr | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Brazil's Vale produced 85.3 mln tonnes of iron ore in 2nd-qtr
text:
RIO DE JANEIRO, July 23 Brazilian mining company Vale SA said on Thursday it produced 85.3 million tonnes of its own iron ore in the second quarter, the second highest quarterly production ever for the firm.
The company also produced 67,100 tonnes of nickel and 2.01 million tonnes of coal in the quarter, the company said in a statement. (Reporting by Stephen Eisenhammer, Editing by Franklin Paul)
